Title: chip_atlas_promoters_f5
Description: An intersection matrix describing overlaps between ChIP-Atlas's ChIP-seq tracks and promoters_f5. To find overlapping regions promoters were extended by 500bp in both directions.

Title: remap_promoters_f5
Description: An intersection matrix describing overlaps between ReMap2020's ChIP-seq tracks and promoters_f5. To find overlapping regions promoters were extended by 500bp in both directions.

Title: promoters_f5
Description: FANTOM5's hg38 promoters annotated with nearest features in GENCODE ver. 38 annotation and UCSC hg38 knownGene annotation ver. 3.13.0.

Title: promoters_f5_core
Description: Core promoters selected from promoters_f5. Selection criteria were GENCODE confirmation and ENCODE ROADMAP confirmation. Further for each gene single promoter with highest FANTOM5 score was selected.
